resources.string: Almost all generators or templates are very limited. They usually have limited phrasing and/or limit how many clauses you can include. Most likely, the generators will not work for you. Your company is unique and your privacy policy should be geared specifically toward your situation. The chances of a generator actually producing the language and clauses you need are pretty slim. Free usually isn’t really free. Most of these sites offer a very basic option before they ask you to upgrade for a higher fee. Consider what you really gain here. You will be paying for something that may or may not actually work for you.
